Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper introduces a logical system derived from linear logic. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is also likely as the paper discusses a concrete GoI interpretation, which is related to programming languages. 
- cs.ET (Emerging Technologies) is a possible category as quantum computing is an emerging technology. 
- cs.QI (Quantum Physics) is another possible category as the paper deals with quantum circuits and their relationship with a logical system. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper discusses the ability of the logical system to capture all unitary quantum circuits.
